= SDL_NumHaptics =
Use this function to count the number of __joysticks__ attached to the system.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_NumHaptics(void)
```

== Return Value ==
Returns the number of __haptic__ devices detected on the system, or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

